ICON LIBRARY V4B -
Icolib is a collection of over 5,400 icons
(10,200 when you register) which have been
stored according to category. There are very
few duplicate icons. An icon viewer is
included with following features: User
configured menu, icon animation, change
background color, extract icon from library,
cascading menus, full help. Requires Win 3.1
or Windows 95 and COMMDLG.DLL (included).
